'''T-3000'''為一名「[[魔鬼終結者系列電影|魔鬼終結者系列電影]]」中的[[人形機器人|人形機器人]]角色，同時也是該系列的第五部作品《[[魔鬼終結者：創世契機|魔鬼終結者：創世契機]]》中的反派<ref>{{cite web|url=http://movieweb.com/terminator-genisys-posters-characters-t-3000/|title=‘Terminator Genisys’ Character Posters Introduce the T-3000 -- Jason Clarke's John Connor is not who he seems in a set of 5 ‘Terminator Genisys’ posters that show off each generation of cyborg.|publisher=[[movieweb.com|movieweb.com]]|accessdate=2015-07-07|date=2015-05-09|first=ALAN|last=ORANGE|archive-date=2015-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706062523/http://movieweb.com/terminator-genisys-posters-characters-t-3000/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/terminator-genisys-posters-present-t3000/|title=Terminator Genisys Posters Present The T-3000|publisher=wegotthiscovered.com|accessdate=2015-07-07|date=|first=Isaac|last=Feldber|archive-date=2015-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714153405/http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/terminator-genisys-posters-present-t3000/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/What-Exactly-John-Connor-Terminator-Genisys-70857.html|title=What Exactly Is John Connor In Terminator: Genisys?|publisher=cinemablend.com|accessdate=2015-07-07|date=|first=GREGORY|last=WAKEMAN|archive-date=2015-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707201344/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/What-Exactly-John-Connor-Terminator-Genisys-70857.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://moviepilot.com/posts/2015/02/03/terminator-5-genisys-storyline-revealed-2653687?lt_source=external,manual|title=Terminator 5: Genisys Storyline Revealed!|publisher=[[moviepilot.com|moviepilot.com]]|accessdate=2015-07-07|date=2015-02-03|first=Jim|last=Galizia|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150710084804/http://moviepilot.com/posts/2015/02/03/terminator-5-genisys-storyline-revealed-2653687?lt_source=external,manual|archivedate=2015-07-10}}</ref>。

T-3000的唯一使命是保護和確保[[天網_(魔鬼終結者)|天網]]的安全。T-3000自我描述本身既不是機器也不是人類的存在<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bleedingcool.com/2015/04/13/im-not-machine-im-not-man-im-more-new-trailer-for-terminator-genisys/|publisher=bleedingcool.com|title="I'm Not Machine, I'm Not Man... I'm More." - New Trailer For Terminator Genisys|accessdate=2015-07-08|date=2015-04-13|first=Dan|last=Wickline|8=|archive-date=2015-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708202044/http://www.bleedingcool.com/2015/04/13/im-not-machine-im-not-man-im-more-new-trailer-for-terminator-genisys/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。監製{{link-en|大衛·艾里森|David Ellison}}解釋說，電影標題《魔鬼終結者：創世契機》是象徵著[[技術奇異點|技術奇異點]]和{{link-en|後人類|Posthuman|人機混合體}}的約翰·康納而來。

== 人物 ==
當人類反抗軍將擊敗人工智能[[天網_(魔鬼終結者)|天網]]時，天網製造了一個臨時的實體[[T-5000|T-5000]]並偽裝成反抗軍，命名「艾力克斯」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joblo.com/movie-news/rumor-matt-smiths-terminator-genisys-role-revealed-844|publisher=[[joblo.com|joblo.com]]|title=-MATT SMITH'S TERMINATOR- GENISYS ROLE REVEALED|accessdate=2015-07-08|first=Jesse|last=Giroux|archive-date=2015-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709053226/http://www.joblo.com/movie-news/rumor-matt-smiths-terminator-genisys-role-revealed-844|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/456251-matt-smiths-terminator-genisys-character-explained|publisher=comingsoon.com|title=Matt Smith’s Terminator Genisys Character Explained|accessdate=2015-07-08|first=SILAS|last=LESNICK|date=2015-07-02|archive-date=2015-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150820055607/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/456251-matt-smiths-terminator-genisys-character-explained|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在天網戰敗後、[[凱爾·瑞斯|凱爾·瑞斯]]被[[約翰·康納|約翰·康納]]送回1984年以防止終結者暗殺[[莎拉·康纳|莎拉·康纳]]時，「艾力克斯」突然襲擊了約翰，他殺死了在場的所有的士兵並將約翰的身體細胞感染[[奈米|奈米]]機器，使其成為新終結者「T-3000」。約翰·康納的轉變之事件使原有[[时间轴|-{zh-hant:時間線; zh-cn:时间轴;}-]]被改變分歧，這徹底[[追溯連續性|改寫了過去和未來]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://consequenceofsound.net/2015/06/film-review-terminator-genisys/|publisher=consequenceofsound.net|title=Film Review: Terminator Genisys|accessdate=2015-07-08|first=MICHAEL|last=ROFFMANON|date=2015-06-30|archive-date=2015-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704015112/http://consequenceofsound.net/2015/06/film-review-terminator-genisys/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="IGN">{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/terminator-genisys-sequels-jai-courtney/|title=Jai Courtney Calls TERMINATOR GENISYS a "Reset" for the Franchise; Says You Don’t Have to Have Seen the Previous Films to Understand It|publisher=Collider|date=2014-10-12|accessdate=2015-07-11|archive-date=2015-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708080855/http://collider.com/terminator-genisys-sequels-jai-courtney/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

T-3000被送回2014年，而被賦予的使命是協助賽博丹公司開發新系統「創世紀（Genisys）」，「創世紀」同時也是天網的前身。當莎拉和凱爾回到2017年時，T-3000說服他們自己真的是約翰，但其偽裝被[[魔鬼終結者_(電影角色)|守-{}-護者]]識破。後來，T-3000對三人展開了一連串的追殺；最後被守-{}-護者困於時間機器中而使身體被瓦解消滅{{notetag|其身體被守-{}-護者以自製的磁石拳套干擾，而無法變化成人皮型態，加上搭乘時空機時若攜金屬物搭乘會產生爆炸。}}。

此外，守-{}-護者於電影中曾解釋，在試圖製造T-3000時造成許多試驗者發瘋和死亡，而約翰是唯一已知受感染後的生存者。

== 能力 ==
以奈米級磁粉組成的T-3000具有高度先進的能力，包括高速移動、奈米體分解與組裝和[[變身|變身]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thewrap.com/terminator-genisys-review-arnold-schwarzenegger-emilia-clarke-jason-clarke-jai-courtney/|publisher=thewrap.com|title=‘Terminator Genisys’ Review: Arnold Schwarzenegger’s Swagger Can’t Save This Redundant Tentpole|accessdate=2015-07-08|date=2015-06-24|first=James|last=Rocchi|archive-date=2015-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705064820/http://www.thewrap.com/terminator-genisys-review-arnold-schwarzenegger-emilia-clarke-jason-clarke-jai-courtney/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了子彈與一般火藥無法傷及外，其變化能力遠超越[[T-1000|T-1000]]，能[[變身|完全仿製他人外表與肢體、說話方式]]。加上還擁有原人類宿主的記憶和個性，T-3000滲透的能力勝於以往的終結者。但不能像T-5000一樣，無法感染他人以創造更多的T-3000。其弱點為高密度強磁場會干擾體內的磁粉運作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://theweirdrobot.com/2015/07/03/review-terminator-genisys/|publisher=theweirdrobot.com|title=REVIEW: Terminator Genisys|accessdate=2015-07-08|date=2015-07-03|first=|last=|archive-date=2015-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709012913/http://theweirdrobot.com/2015/07/03/review-terminator-genisys/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，同時雖然原作沒有提及，但可以推論摧毀T-1000的高溫溶爐一樣能破壞它。

